## Mental Model

**Retention requires job frequency.**

If the core job isn't frequent, MRR collapses after the initial honeymoon. Every feature/product must include a "JTBD Frequency Map." If the job is rare, you need frequency boosters (critical alerts, batching workflows, periodic review cycles) to keep the product alive.
